Eu era amigo de Yeong Rye
na Cheongah Transportation.

00:43:00.630 --> 00:43:03.060
Jong Hui?

00:43:03.060 --> 00:43:05.530
Aquele que costumava vir a nossa casa?

00:43:05.530 --> 00:43:09.110
Sim. Sou eu. Jong Hui.

